### `category_splits` — RLS ⚠️ disabled

Defines default percentage splits per `expense_category` per `household_member`. When an expense is filed under a category, these splits determine who owes what unless overridden.

| Column | Type | Nullable | Default | Notes |
|--------|------|----------|---------|-------|
| `id` | uuid | NO | `gen_random_uuid()` | PK |
| `category_id` | uuid | NO | — | FK → `expense_categories.id` |
| `household_member_id` | uuid | NO | — | FK → `household_members.id` |
| `percentage` | numeric | NO | — | CHECK 0–100. This member's share of that category |

