### `expense_splits` — RLS ⚠️ disabled

Per-member breakdown of what each member owes for a given expense. Rows are generated when an expense is created. Mirrors `category_splits` unless overridden.

| Column | Type | Nullable | Default | Notes |
|--------|------|----------|---------|-------|
| `id` | uuid | NO | `gen_random_uuid()` | PK |
| `expense_id` | uuid | NO | — | FK → `expenses.id` |
| `household_member_id` | uuid | NO | — | FK → `household_members.id` |
| `percentage_override` | numeric | YES | — | CHECK 0–100. If set, overrides the category default split |
| `calculated_amount` | numeric | NO | — | CHECK >= 0. Computed dollar amount this member owes |
| `is_settled` | boolean | NO | `false` | Whether this member has paid back their share |

